.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/FYEV/110%2c%e8%b1%90%e7%b0%a1%2c863%2c20220223%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"FYEV,110,豐簡,863,20220223,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"豐簡","JNO":"863","JDATE":"20220223","JTITLE":"清償借款"}